\c 49
\s Chirevo pamusoro paAmoni
\p
\v 1 Pamusoro peVaAmoni. Anoreva seizvi Jehovha. Israeri haana vanakomana here? Haana mugari wenhaka here? Sei Marikami agara nhaka yaGadhi, vanhu vake vachigara mumaguta ake?
\v 2 Naizvozvo tarira, mazuva anouya, anoreva Jehovha, andichanzwisa mhere yehondo muRabha revana vaAmoni; uye richaitwa murwi wematongo; uye vakunda varo vachapiswa nemoto, zvino achava mugari wenhaka kune vaiva vagri venhaka vake, anoreva Jehovha.
\p
\v 3 Ungudza iwe Heshibhoni, nokuti Ai raparadzwa, chemai imwi vakunda vaRebha, zvisungei zviuno nemasaga, ungudzai, muende uko neuko pauzhowa, nokuti Marikami achaenda muutapwa, vapristi vake nemachinda ake pamwe chete.
\v 4 Unozvikudzirei mumipata, mupata wako unoyerera, iwe mukunda wekudzokera shure? Anovimba nefuma yake \add achiti\add*: Ndiani achauya kwandiri?
\v 5 Tarira, ndichauisa chityiso pamusoro pako, anoreva Jehovha wehondo, kubva kune vese vakakukomberedza, uye muchadzingwa murume umwe neumwe pamberi pake, uye hakuna achaunganidza anodzungaira.
\v 6 Zvino pashure ndichadzosa utapwa hwevana vaAmoni, anoreva Jehovha.
\p
\v 7 Pamusoro paEdhomu, anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo: Hakuchina uchenjeri muTemani here? Zano rapera here kune vanonzwisisa? Uchenjeri hwavo hwanyangarika here?
\v 8 Tizai, dzokai shure, garai makadzika, vagari vepaDhedhani; nokuti ndichauisa dambudziko raEsau pamusoro pake, nguva yekumushanyira kwangu.
\v 9 Kana vakohwi vemazambiringa vakasvika kwauri, havangasii mazambiringa zvekufuhurudza here? Kana mbavha \add dzikasvika\add* usiku, havangaparadzi kusvika vakwana here?
\v 10 Asi ini ndafukura Esau, ndazarura nzvimbo dzake dzechivande, kuti asagona kuzvivanza, chizvarwa chake chatapwa, nehama dzake nevavakidzani vake, iye haachipo.
\v 11 Siya nherera dzako, ini ndichadzichengeta dzichirarama, nechirikadzi dzako ngadzivimbe neni.
\p
\v 12 Nokuti anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Tarirai, kunyange vemutongo wavo waiva wekusanwa pamukombe vakanwa zvekunwa; zvino iwe ndiwe ucharegwa chose usingarangwi here? Haungaregwi usina mhosva, asi uchanwa zvirokwazvo.
\v 13 Nokuti ndakapika neni ndomene, anoreva Jehovha, kuti Bhozira richava chityiso, ive chishoorwa, dongo, uye chakatukwa, nemaguta aro ese achava matongo nekusingaperi.
\p
\v 14 Ndakanzwa shoko kubva kuna Jehovha, uye nhume yakatumwa pakati pemarudzi, ichiti: Unganai, muuye kuzorirwisa, uye simukirai hondo.
\v 15 Nokuti tarira, ndakakuita mudiki pakati pemarudzi, neanozvidzwa pakati pevanhu.
\v 16 Kutyisa kwako kwakunyengera, kuzvikudza kwemoyo wako, iwe ugere mumokaha yedombo, wakabata nhongonya yechikomo, kunyange ukaita dendere rako rakakwirira segondo, ndichakuburusa kubvapo, anoreva Jehovha.
\p
\v 17 NaEdhomu richaitwa chityiso, uye ani nani anopfuura pariri achashamiswa kwazvo, uye achiridzira muridzo matambudziko aro ese.
\v 18 Sapakutsindikirwa kweSodhoma neGomora nemaguta akavakidzana nawo, anoreva Jehovha, hakuna munhu achagaramo, uye hakuna mwanakomana wemunhu achagara mariri semutorwa.
\v 19 Tarira, achakwira seshumba achibva pakukukumara kwaJoridhani kurwisa ugaro hweakasimba, asi ndichamumhanyisa pakarepo kubva kwaari; zvino ndiani wakasarudzwa wandichagadza pamusoro pake? Nokuti ndiani wakaita seni? Uye ndiyani achandigadzira nguva? Uye ndiani mufudzi achamira pamberi pangu?
\p
\v 20 Naizvozvo inzwai zano raJehovha raakatora kurwisa Edhomu, nechinangwa chake chaakananga kurwisa vagari veTemani: Zvirokwazvo vadikisa veboka vachavakweva, zvirokwazvo ugaro hwavo huchaparadzwa pamusoro pavo.
\v 21 Nyika inodederaeruzha rwekuwa kwavo, pakuchema ruzha rwavo rwakasvika kuGungwa Dzvuku.
\v 22 Tarira, achakwira ndokubhururuka segondo, ndokutandavadza mapapiro ake pamusoro peBhozira, zvino pazuva iro moyo wevane simba veEdhomu uchava semoyo wemukadzi pakurwadziwa kwake nemimba.
\s Chirevo pamusoro peDhamasiko
\p
\v 23 Pamusoro peDhamasiko. Hamati ranyadziswa, neAripadhi, nokuti vakanzwa mashoko akaipa, vakanyauka; kusuruvara kuri pagungwa, harigoni kunyarara.
\v 24 Dhamasiko rapera simba, rakatendeukira kutiza, kutya kwaribata, kumanikidzwa, nekushungurudzika kwaribata seanorwadziwa nemimba.
\v 25 Harina kusiiwa sei guta rekurumbidzwa, guta remufaro wangu?
\v 26 Naizvozvo majaya aro achawira munzira dzaro dzemumusha, nevarume vese vehondo vachagurwa pazuva iro, anoreva Jehovha wehondo.
\v 27 Zvino ndichabatidza moto murusvingo rweDhamasiko, uye uchaparadza mizinda yaBheni-Hadhadhi.
\s Chirevo pamusoro paKedhari neHazori
\p
\v 28 Pamusoro paKedhari nepamusoro peushe hweHazori hwakarohwa naNebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi: Anoreva seizvi Jehovha: Simukai, kwirai kuKedhari, munoparadza varume vekumabvazuva.
\v 29 Vachatora matende avo nemapoka avo emakwai, maketeni avo nemidziyo, nemakamera avo vachazvitakurirako, vachadanidzira kwavari \add vachiti\add*: Zvityiso kumativi ese!
\v 30 Tizai, mudzungaire kwazvo, garai makadzika, imwi vagari veHazori, anoreva Jehovha; nokuti Nebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi wakaronga zano kukurwisai, wakakufungirai mufungo wakaipa.
\v 31 Simukai, muende kundorwa norudzi rwakazorora, runogara rusina hanya, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha; rusina masuwo kana zvipfigiso, runogara rwega.
\v 32 Makamera avo achatapwa nezvipfuwo zvavo zvizhinji zvichapambiwa; ndichavaparadzira kumativi ese kunobva mhepo, ivo vakaveurwa mativi evhudzi ravo, ndichavauyisira njodzi yavo ichibva kumativi ese ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 33 Hazori huchava hugaro hwamakava, nedongo nokusingaperi; hakuna munhu ungagaramo, hakuna mwanakomana womunhu uchavamo ari mutorwa.
\s Chirevo pamusoro paEramu
\p
\v 34 Shoko raJehovha, rakasvika kumuporofita Jeremiya pamusoro paEramu, pakutanga kokubata ushe kwaZedhekia mambo waJudha, richiti:
\v 35 Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo: Tarirai, ndichavhuna huta hwaEramu, icho chinhu chikuru chesimba ravo.
\v 36 Ndichauyisira pamusoro paEramu mhepo ina dzichibva kumativi mana okudenga, ndichavaparadzira kumativi iwo mana kunobva mhepo; hakungavi norudzi rumwe kusingasviki ivo vakadzingwa vaEramu.
\v 37 Ndichavhundusa Eramu pamberi pavavengi vavo napamberi pavanotsvaka kuvauraya; ndichauisa zvakaipa pamusoro pavo, iko kutsamwa kwangu kukuru, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha; ndichatuma munondo uvateverere kusvikira ndavapedza.
\v 38 Ndichaisa chigaro changu choushe maEramu, ndiparadze mambo namachinda vabvepo ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\p
\v 39 Asi namazuva okupedzisira ndichadzosazve kutapwa kwaEramu, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
